<% const pageTitle = "Refund & Cancellation Policy – VK Training Consultency"; %>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Refund &amp; Cancellation Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10">Last updated: 25 April 2026</p>

  <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">1. Overview</h2>
      <p>VK Training Consultency is committed to ensuring satisfaction with every purchase. Please read this policy carefully before making a purchase. By completing a transaction on our Platform, you agree to the terms below.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">2. Refund Eligibility</h2>
      <p>You may request a refund under the following conditions:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>The request is made within <strong>7 days</strong> of the original purchase date.</li>
        <li>You have not accessed or watched more than <strong>20%</strong> of the course content.</li>
        <li>The course is technically inaccessible due to a platform error and the issue was not resolved within 72 hours of reporting.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">3. Non-Refundable Situations</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Refund requests made after 7 days of purchase.</li>
        <li>Courses where more than 20% of the content has been consumed.</li>
        <li>Purchases made using promotional discounts or special offer codes, unless the course is technically defective.</li>
        <li>Duplicate purchases — please contact us immediately and we will cancel the duplicate order instead.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">4. How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Email <a href="mailto:support@vktraining.in" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@vktraining.in</a> with the subject line: <em>Refund Request – [Your Order ID]</em>.</li>
        <li>Include your registered email address, order/payment ID, and the reason for the refund request.</li>
        <li>Our team will review your request and respond within <strong>3 business days</strong>.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">5. Refund Processing</h2>
      <p>Approved refunds are processed via Razorpay back to the original payment instrument:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Credit/Debit Cards:</strong> 5–7 business days after approval.</li>
        <li><strong>UPI / Net Banking / Wallets:</strong> 3–5 business days after approval.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-2">Actual credit timelines depend on your bank or payment provider and are outside our control once initiated.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">6. Cancellation of Subscription / Access</h2>
      <p>Since courses are sold on a one-time pay-per-access basis (not a recurring subscription), there is no recurring billing to cancel. Access remains active for the period stated at the time of purchase. If you wish to close your account, email us and we will deactivate it after settling any pending refund or affiliate claims.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">7. Affiliate Commission Reversal</h2>
      <p>If a sale that generated an affiliate commission is refunded, the corresponding commission will be reversed from the affiliate's pending balance.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">8. Chargebacks</h2>
      <p>If you raise a chargeback with your bank without first contacting us, we reserve the right to suspend your account pending investigation and to dispute the chargeback with supporting evidence.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">9. Contact</h2>
      <p><strong>VK Training Consultency</strong><br />
      Email: <a href="mailto:support@vktraining.in" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@vktraining.in</a><br />
      Response time: within 3 business days</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
